These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the argentine##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

