.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the bartender is the person eating onion##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the photographer##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

