.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, indie, jazz, metal, r&b, rock
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the fan of metal is the australian##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the fan of indie is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
11. the thai is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | rock     | jazz     | indie      | folk | metal      | disco     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

