.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, drawing, gardening, magic-tricks, sudoku, video-games
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

