.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk   | 7up | iced-tea | sprite  | juice | almond-milk |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

