.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, drama, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | time-travel | drama | martial-arts | satire     | animation | crime |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

