 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

