The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, martial-arts, musical, romance, sports
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | chess   | singing | baking | puzzles | gardening | fishing  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | musical | sports  | family | romance | crime     | disaster |

